1. Encode the SVG into a base64 string

2. Embed it as an on-chain NFT using the tokenURI() method

Okay so when we were using the IPFS, so as we are not doing it on IPFS and we have to do it in a SVG
and what we can do is we can take a SVG and we need to base64 encode it using "base64 -i Happy.svg"
and then after we base64 encode this string right here we need to convert it to tokenURI
by doing "data:image/svg+xml;base64,<base64-encoded SVG>"

